{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c85d81683c","title":"中联部、外交部关于召开外事会议的请示报告和周恩来的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0ed6cd936a","index":0,"year":1972,"month":11,"day":28,"articleId":"c85d81683c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"江青","id":"82305e518c","type":"人物"},{"name":"各部、委文件","id":"958167f230","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"批示","id":"9bc2c334c7","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"耿飚","id":"f811dad292","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bdc20c6d19","type":"title","text":"中联部、外交部关于召开外事会议的请示报告和周恩来的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee9922c37e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理并中央：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33491f4ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"在毛主席的革命外交路线指引下和中央的正确领导下，我国在外交战线上取得了重大胜利，对外工作发展很快。但是，外事工作中还存在着许多亟待解决的问题。主要是林彪反党集团煽动的极“左\"思潮在一些单位和地方还没有得到彻底批判和肃清，中央的方针政策在一些环节上还没有得到认真贯彻落实。外事工作体制，外事工作队伍的状况和一些规章制度不能适应日益发展的工作需要。在接待工作、口岸工作、归侨和外国人的管理工作等方面都存在着不少问题。为了解决这些问题，拟于近期召开一次全国外事工作会议。现将关于会议的几个设想报告如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c6786d4bd","type":"paragraph","text":"一、会议的任务：联系外事工作的实际，以批林整风为纲，彻底批判林彪反党集团煽动的极“左”思潮和无政府主义，研究和解决外事工作中的一些迫切问题，以便更好地贯彻执行毛主席的革命外交路线。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"18677ba797","type":"paragraph","text":"……","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35d274eedf","type":"paragraph","text":"以上意见当否，请批示。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78ec796bfb","type":"paragraph","text":"中  联  部","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cd27f1a9d","type":"paragraph","text":"外  交  部","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"35c8de2dbf","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年十二月二十八日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a16b992ad","type":"paragraph","text":"拟同意，请送耿飚同志会签后，再呈主席、康生（暂不送）、江青、春桥、文元、剑英、先念、登奎、德生、东兴、洪文同志批示。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d964462cb2","type":"paragraph","text":"周  恩  来","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e34009c9d","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年十一月三十日","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3fd2f2695b","type":"paragraph","text":"附件一：","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6aeda89ed","type":"paragraph","text":"张春桥的批语","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abc267c5de","type":"paragraph","text":"送江青同志、总理再阅","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"053f00abeb","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2cbbec797","type":"paragraph","text":"我不了解外事工作的全面情况，但是，当前的主要问题是否仍然是极“左”思潮？批林是否就是批极“左”和无政府主义？我正在考虑。建议外事会议批林要批得全面一些，同时要讨论毛主席关于深挖洞、广积粮、不称霸的指示。妥否，供参考。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6961bba9d7","type":"paragraph","text":"春    桥","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d3cd1eb83b","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年十二月一日","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1ab9f3dcbd","type":"paragraph","text":"附件二：","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6408d0b82e","type":"paragraph","text":"江青的批语","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1001939614","type":"paragraph","text":"我个人认为应批林彪卖国贼的极右，同时批他在某些问题上形左实右。在批林彪叛徒的同时也应着重讲一下无产阶级文化大革命的胜利。因为，没有这次无产阶级文化大革命，暴露不出他们来，他们还隐藏下来，那对我们党和人民将造成很大的损失。当然，天也塌不下来。","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8092c9b08","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七二年十二月二日","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e55022b756","type":"paragraph","text":"供总理参考。又及","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"874b985867","type":"paragraph","text":"注：此件是中央办公厅秘书局提供的。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"c85d81683c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}